org.dockbox.selene.core.impl.events

Class InvokeWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dockbox.selene.core.impl.events.InvokeWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<InvokeWrapper>, IWrapper

    public class InvokeWrapper
extends Object
implements Comparable<InvokeWrapper>, IWrapper
    Wrapper type for future invokation of a Method listening for Event posting. This type is responsible for filtering and invoking a Method when a supported Event is fired.

        public static List<InvokeWrapper> create(Object instance,
                                         Method method,
                                         int priority)
        Creates one or more InvokeWrappers (depending on how many event parameters are present) for a given method and instance.
        Parameters:
        instance - The instance which is used when invoking the method.
        method - The method to store for invokation.
        priority - The priority at which the event is fired.
        Returns:
